com.attivio.sdk.schema

Class FieldNames

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.attivio.sdk.schema.FieldNames

  • public class FieldNames
extends Object
    Contains document field names that are frequently used in the default Attivio transformers. Components can use different and/or non-defined field names however these are the defaults for all Attivio supplied transformers.
